title: {Godprop #14} Yomopu Expansion
body:
If this proposal passes:

The following pools will be added to yomopu in accordance to Prop 4.

1. YORO - deposit fees will be hodl'd
2. CATNIP - deposit fees will be burned to the deady
3. WFTM - deposit fees will be unwrapped (5%) for gas fees, (95%) will be added to cream
4. LINK - deposit fees will be added to cream (we'll need this for future use of their verifiable randomness jazz)

YORO & CATNIP's farm for ECHO-FTM on zoodex brought us great exposure, and resulted in us landing a vault on grim. By adding YORO & CATNIP single stake to yomopu we can further increase the value we bring to their ecosystem.
